eya]]\n| f\n| [[Wood Memorial Stakes]], [[Pilgrim Stakes]], [[Fountain of Youth Stakes]]\n|-\n| 2009\n| Creative Cause\n| c\n| [[American Pharoah Stakes]], [[San Felipe Stakes]]\n|-\n| 2009\n| Irish Mission\n| c\n| [[Glens Falls Stakes]], [[La Prevoyante Stakes (Gulfstream Park) | La Prevoyante Stakes]]\n|-\n| 2010\n| Rite of Passage\n| c\n| [[Ascot Gold Cup]] \n|-\n| 2010\n| Red Rifle\n| c\n| [[Bowling Green Handicap]], [[Dominion Day Stakes]] \n|-\n| 2011\n| Protonico\n| c\n| [[Alysheba Stakes]], [[Discovery Handicap]]\n|-\n| 2012\n| Take Charge Brandi\n| c\n| [[Breeders' Cup Juvenile Fillies]] \n|-\n| 2013\n| [[Brody's Cause]]\n| c\n| [[Breeders' Futurity Stakes]], [[Blue Grass Stakes]]\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[Bricks and Mortar]]\n| c\n| [[Manhattan Handicap]], [[Turf Classic Stakes]], [[Pegasus World Cup Turf]], [[Arlington Million]], [[Breeders' Cup Turf]]\n|}\n\n==Pedigree==\n{{Pedigree\n|name = Giant's Causeway \n|f = [[Storm Cat]]\n|m = [[Mariah's Storm]]\n|ff = [[Storm Bird]]\n|fm = [[Terlingua (horse)|Terlingua]]\n|mf = [[Rahy]]\n|mm = Immense\n|fff = [[Northern Dancer]]\n|ffm = South Ocean\n|fmf = [[Secretariat (horse)|Secretariat]]\n|fmm = Crimson Saint\n|mff = [[Blushing Groom]]\n|mfm = [[Glorious Song]]\n|mmf = [[Roberto (horse)|Roberto]]\n|mmm = Imsodear\n|ffff = [[Nearctic (horse)|Nearctic]]\n|fffm = [[Natalma]]\n|ffmf = [[New Providence (horse)|New Providence]]\n|ffmm = Shining Sun\n|fmff = [[Bold Ruler]]\n|fmfm = [[Somethingroyal]]\n|fmmf = [[Crimson Satan]]\n|fmmm = Bolero Rose\n|mfff = [[Red God]]\n|mffm = Runaway Bride\n|mfmf = [[Halo (horse)|Halo]]\n|mfmm = Ballade\n|mmff = [[Hail To Reason]]\n|mmfm = Bramalea\n|mmmf = Chieftain\n|mmmm = Ironically\n|}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n* [http://www.pedigreequery.com/giants+causeway Giant's Causeway's pedigree and stats]\n* [http://www.stallionregister.com/sr_sire_page.asp?refno=4297000&origin=singlesearch Giant's Causeway in the Stallion Register]\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.jockeycolours.com